name: Insane Draws
description:
These draws are insane. The effected area follows the mouse cursor. Controls ->

- scroll the mouse wheel to increase/decrease size of effected area
- press 's' to save image as png
- press 't' to cycle through available shape types
- press 'a' to cycle through available angles
- press 'r' to reset and get a new random color
- press 'p' to pause
- press 'd' to cycle through shape dimensions
- press 'f' to cycle through field sizes
- press 'w' to cycle through time warps
